,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:36:20.000Z","msg":"又tvb又地區遊行又memo又廣告，開始人力資源唔集中，太多活動"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:53:25.000Z","msg":"集中一條戰線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:57:16.000Z","msg":"已經好難集中翻，開始各自為政，唔會聽你講"},{"pid":"b43366ce85c7998dfa44614221663728c0326f61","tid":1304162,"uid":265192,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:58:35.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重啟文宣，反駁「壽終正寢」論 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不撤不散，聚焦五大訴求<br />\n停止執著連儂牆，Be Water第日再整過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"},{"pid":"bb983567580c5c882eeb98641d24f9b4470878b4","tid":1304162,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:58:52.000Z","msg":"目前戰線太多，運動重心偏離；大家花太多時間係寶礦力同連儂場上面。<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我地需要集中火力係五大訴求上面。</span></span></strong>只有個議題仲係度，個運動先繼續有力量做其他野。重心要放返係「送中」上面，連帶反黑警；連儂場唔好太執著、反TVB唔好反多過林鄭。先搞「送中」，燈柱同信用評分先慢慢普及。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">重心一定要放返係「送中」上面！</span></strong>"},{"pid":"8a011bd37348a3a8b3b3a80638f3a2d9384b0f27","tid":1304162,"uid":265192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:59:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/y89X0ke.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fy89X0ke.png&h=5453cdeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8On3brV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8On3brV.png&h=c2b4f58e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f03541300528f4d31be4814329f13d1c86fa2a13","tid":1304162,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:59:16.000Z","msg":"有意義討論post 推"},{"pid":"160e6ee7f4991d784173c6053fe0076d98facb28","tid":1304162,"uid":142332,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7258af878d6fda66d9f246d6e2230d751434d184","tid":1304162,"uid":170974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T13:59:30.000Z","msg":"依家黑警八卦野上哂熱門<br />\n<br />\n外國以為轉地贏左 淺黃覺得已勝<br />\n<br />\n監控cctv 我地既手足都未救<br />\n<br />\n依家開太多戰線 自己打亂左自己啦 學生過左暑假 仲有幾多成年人肯同你個個星期衝 個個星期遊行<br />\n<br />\n我地已經無得再輸 林鄭對上兩次記者會擺到明攞黎哄人搞分化 呃外國傳媒<br />\n我地五大訴求一句佢都無應承過！<br />\n個黑警 搶哂focus 啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">又話有post 登報反外交部 又話同外國傳媒澄清我地未贏既？<br />\n咁多條人命200萬人遊行 咁多手足比人搵 壽終正寢就夠？</span></span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T14:59:45.000Z","msg":"呢個係一個英雄四起,百花齊放既時代<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1292200\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1292200</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"36e156cd5fccd179ca40d51137397cdb65285d38","tid":1304162,"uid":258696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:00:59.000Z","msg":"文宣組"},{"pid":"d533d223b24f49741f3892a4ad5b98ea69667626","tid":1304162,"uid":163252,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:01:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6e55367e966936910e6401c9d8fccb0136cd09e0","tid":1304162,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:04:16.000Z","msg":"對外賣新聞 要睇攬炒巴<br />\n<br />\n暫時係 成立獨委會 同 唔控告暴動 係有社會最大的共識<br />\n問題係個個大Topic每個人的排序唔同<br />\n有人認為撤回最重要<br />\n有人認為特赦最重要<br />\n有人認為查警最重要<br />\n有人認為收暴動最重要<br />\n有人認為應該開新路線_普選-紅媒<br />\n<br />\n變相遊行大主題唔係自己最睇重個樣 參與度就會差佐<br />\n<br />\n大家都無咩共識 所以就自然變成有咩都做吓 好散<br />\n因為而家散唔重家top topi"},{"pid":"191dc62396d92ab6f21ff04b4059afecd03695ee","tid":1304162,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T15:04:42.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cb7d0fc93d9e8346b82d5c92b48162ce53efeb2b","tid":1304162,"uid":258696,"like":0,"disl