ih.kg/1300395</a><br />\n<br />\n［信你一成］政府澄清，不會在香港施行社會信用體系。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1300401\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1300401</a><br />\n<br />\n［社會信用體系］我真係唔撚同你講笑，禁入去拉到最底睇下，港豬<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1300241\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1300241</a><br />\n<br />\n政制及內地事務局局長聶德權： 信用制度不會在港實施<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1300116\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1300116</a>"},{"pid":"74554675064c2602292082dd08da6194033b8e24","tid":1304162,"uid":58041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:06:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4033afca48f33a2c6d54d28b310e373793fe83af","tid":1304162,"uid":25044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T03:07:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2efc43067889091138a58372b3edaf5a0c12215d","tid":1304162,"uid":276020,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:27:36.000Z","msg":"［文宣］有D係時候要講清楚啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1305188\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1305188</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"0fb1f4e7141f0c551de93e392677444753c4d8d4","tid":1304162,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T04:28:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa64dca854d04b804199d7683953aad24c85f100","tid":1304162,"uid":104160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:08:56.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"d573e5e1f6b403dad4b2c7f6850d56405a9e88ee","tid":1304162,"uid":104160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:09:08.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"c27013d9e9fb985c83345badd142364bd2bd2ddf","tid":1304162,"uid":260325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:14:02.000Z","msg":"我地輸緊5比0"},{"pid":"8a2aff94a9fa28b1e61e29654b9c17bb5b4c27bf","tid":1304162,"uid":37528,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T05:1